description:
You got this water bottle from your class trip to
Montreal, Canada. Juan put ketchup in it once...
name: Montreal Water Bottle

description: Waliullah's favorite erasable pen. So cool!
name: Erasable Pen

description:
Just a random stick Juan found on the ground. You're
amazed by how quickly he found a weapon.
name: Wooden Stick

description: A gun from Daniel's favorite game, Team Fortress 2.
name: TF2 Gun

description:
A plush of Charkis, the equivalent of Chara/Ralsei from
Deltarune: Chapter Rewritten.
name: Charkis Plush

description:
The bubbles Adrianna makes are suprisingly powerful.
Honestly unsure how many gum strips she has.
name: Bubble Gum

description:
The Master Sword, from the Legend of Zelda! Beck has
the strength to wield it.
name: Master Sword

description:
The Chlamydia Plush. Still don't know why it was named
after a bacteria.
name: Chlamydia Plush

description: Allen's car keys. Jab jab!
name: Car Keys

description:
A scythe covered in all colors of paint. A true weapon
of art, wielded by Aubree.
name: Paint Scythe

description:
A magic keyboard that can hover in the air! You can't
help but feel a bit envious of Josh.
name: Magic Keyboard

description:
A weird contraption... a part of a Cactus that can
generate light, like a flashlight.
name: Cactus Light

description: The Friend Inside You.
name: Pistol

description:
One of the oldest objects in this world. You look
inside the glass, and see something blue...
name: Ancient Wand

description:
While a tool for measuring the length of objects, it
can double as a cool lasso!
name: Measuring Tape

description:
Flashbacks to the numerous times you would almost burn
yourself in Chemistry class. Pardee was not amused.
name: Bunsen Burner

description:
A cup with Pusheen The Cat's face on it! It's made of
metal, so it's a powerful weapon.
name: Pusheen Cup

description:
A regular electric guitar. You know Alvin would be able
to play some sick beats. Chance to lower enemy DEF
name: Electric Guitar

description:
A magical keyboard cover. This would be great for Josh
to use.
name: Keyboard Cover

description:
The drone from when you and Allen took a Drone Technol-
ogy class. Adds the "Drone Attack" skill.
name: Mr. Daley's Drone

description:
It shines brightly, illuminating the world around you.
Guaranteed to lower enemy DEF.
name: Shiny Guitar

description:
You're shocked Max gave his bowling ball to you...
Well, not like you can bowl in this world, right?
name: Bowling Ball

description:
An autistic-- you mean, acoustic guitar. Maybe. You're
not really sure what it is. Chance to lower enemy DEF
name: Autistic Guitar
